      <sentence>
         <text>Cole had given his neighbor a promise that he would keep an eye on her house while she was away.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>When he went there that night with Dylan, it was dark and pretty cold, with a nip of frost in the air.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
		    <text>Inside the house was cold too, but everything was in order.</text>
		    <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
	    </sentence>
	   <sentence>
		  <text>Suddenly, the boys heard a noise outside.</text>
		  <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
